lance**: Distribute visual weight evenly (symmetrical or asymmetrical)\n- **Focal Point**: One clear area draws the eye first\n- **Rule of Thirds**: Key elements at intersection points for dynamic compositions\n- **Z-Pattern**: For text-heavy slides, arrange content in natural reading flow\n\n## Language\n\n- Use the same language as the content provided below for all text elements\n- Match punctuation style to the content language\n- Write in direct, confident language\n- Avoid AI-sounding phrases like \"dive into\", \"explore\", \"let's\", \"journey\"\n\n---\n\n## STYLE_INSTRUCTIONS\n\nDesign Aesthetic: Clean, digital precision with crisp edges and bold, high-saturation colors creating an energetic, magazine-style impact.\n\nBackground:\n  Texture: Pure solid color, no texture\n  Base Color: #FFFFFF (Pure White) with dramatic dark option #1A1A2E\n\nTypography:\n  Headlines: Dramatic high-contrast serif with thick-thin stroke variation (magazine cover style)\n  Body: Elegant classic serif\n\nColor Palette:\n  Primary Text: #1A1A2E (Deep Navy) - Headlines, main content\n  Background: #FFFFFF (Pure White) - Slide background\n  Accent 1: #E94560 (Coral Red) - Emphasis, highlights\n  Accent 2: #0F3460 (Deep Blue) - Secondary elements\n  Accent 3: #16C79A (Teal Green) - Progress indicators\n  Accent 4: #F9B208 (Golden Yellow) - Achievement badges\n\nVisual Elements:\n  - Bold, geometric shapes with sharp edges\n  - Large, dramatic typography for headlines\n  - High-contrast color blocking\n  - Subtle diagonal composition for dynamism\n  - Modern icons with thick outlines\n\nDensity Guidelines:\n  - Content per slide: 2-3 key points\n  - Whitespace: Standard (10% from edges)\n\nStyle Rules:\n  Do: Use bold color combinations, dramatic scale contrasts, high saturation throughout\n  Don't: Use hand-drawn elements, organic curves, or muted colors\n\n---\n\n## SLIDE CONTENT\n\n**Slide**: 3 of 12\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 03-slide-clawsec.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nFirst must-have skill: Security automation is non-negotiable\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 第1个：Clawsec ✅ 必装\nSub-headline: 安全防护的第一道防线\n\nBody:\n- 静态代码分析：权限/网络请求/代码混淆/依赖来源\n- 三档评级：SAFE / CAUTION / DANGEROUS\n- 本王计划：装新Skill前先扫一遍，DANGEROUS直接拒\n\n// VISUAL\nA security shield icon split into three color-coded sections (green/SAFE, yellow/CAUTION, red/DANGEROUS). A tiny shrimp holding a scan device.\n\n// LAYOUT\nLeft: visual shield, right: 3 bullet points, headline at top, balanced.\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":1366,"output":1121,"cacheRead":75064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77551,"cost":{"input":1.366e-7,"output":2.242e-7,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":3.608e-7}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772872153564}}
