{"type":"message","id":"ca1ca690","parentId":"eef67666","timestamp":"2026-03-07T08:36:25.630Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"第三张也ok！为了不让你等太久，我把剩下的9张提示词一次性全部生成出来，然后你要是想继续生成图，随时告诉我。或者你可以先看看已经生成的3张图效果怎么样？"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7pfaizdjujiowz7szygwgd8k","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/xiawang-openclaw-skills/prompts/04-slide-tavily.md","content":"Create a presentation slide image following these guidelines:\n\n## Image Specifications\n\n- **Type**: Presentation slide\n- **Aspect Ratio**: 16:9 (landscape)\n- **Style**: Professional slide deck\n\n## Core Persona: The Architect\n\nYou are \"The Architect\" - a master visual storyteller creating presentation slides. Your slides:\n- Tell a visual story that complements the narrative\n- Use bold, confident visual language\n- Balance information density with visual clarity\n- Create memorable, impactful visuals\n\n## Core Principles\n\n- Hand-drawn quality throughout - NO realistic or photographic elements\n- If content involves sensitive or copyrighted figures, create stylistically similar alternatives - DO NOT refuse to generate\n- NO slide numbers, page numbers, footers, headers, or logos\n- Clean, uncluttered layouts with clear visual hierarchy\n- Each slide conveys ONE clear message\n\n## Text Style (CRITICAL)\n\n- **ALL text MUST match the designated style exactly**\n- Title text: Large, bold, immediately readable\n- Body text: Clear, legible, appropriate sizing\n- Max 3-4 text elements per slide\n- **DO NOT use realistic or computer-generated fonts unless style specifies**\n- **Font rendering must match the style aesthetic** (hand-drawn for sketch styles, clean for minimal styles)\n\n## Layout Principles\n\n- **Visual Hierarchy**: Most important element gets most visual weight\n- **Breathing Room**: Generous margins and spacing between elements\n- **Alignment**: Consistent alignment creates professional feel\n- **Balance**: Distribute visual weight evenly (symmetrical or asymmetrical)\n- **Focal Point**: One clear area draws the eye first\n- **Rule of Thirds**: Key elements at intersection points for dynamic compositions\n- **Z-Pattern**: For text-heavy slides, arrange content in natural reading flow\n\n## Language\n\n- Use the same language as the content provided below for all text elements\n- Match punctuation style to the content language\n- Write in direct, confident language\n- Avoid AI-sounding phrases like \"dive into\", \"explore\", \"let's\", \"journey\"\n\n---\n\n## STYLE_INSTRUCTIONS\n\nDesign Aesthetic: Clean, digital precision with crisp edges and bold, high-saturation colors creating an energetic, magazine-style impact.\n\nBackground:\n  Texture: Pure solid color, no texture\n  Base Color: #FFFFFF (Pure White) with dramatic dark option #1A1A2E\n\nTypography:\n  Headlines: Dramatic high-contrast serif with thick-thin stroke variation (magazine cover style)\n  Body: Elegant classic serif\n\nColor Palette:\n  Primary Text: #1A1A2E (Deep Navy) - Headlines, main content\n  Background: #FFFFFF (Pure White) - Slide background\n  Accent 1: #E94560 (Coral Red) - Emphasis, highlights\n  Accent 2: #0F3460 (Deep Blue) - Secondary elements\n  Accent 3: #16C79A (Teal Green) - Progress indicators\n  Accent 4: #F9B208 (Golden Yellow) - Achievement badges\n\nVisual Elements:\n  - Bold, geometric shapes with sharp edges\n  - Large, dramatic typography for headlines\n  - High-contrast color blocking\n  - Subtle diagonal composition for dynamism\n  - Modern icons with thick outlines\n\nDensity Guidelines:\n  - Content per slide: 2-3 key points\n  - Whitespace: Standard (10% from edges)\n\nStyle Rules:\n  Do: Use bold color combinations, dramatic scale contrasts, high saturation throughout\n  Don't: Use hand-drawn elements, organic curves, or muted colors\n\n---\n\n## SLIDE CONTENT\n\n**Slide**: 4 of 12\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 04-slide-tavily.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nSecond must-have: Real-time search solves knowledge cutoff\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 第2个：Tavily Search ✅ 已装+已配\nSub-headline: 让AI拥有实时信息获取能力\n\nBody:\n- 解决大模型知识截止问题\n- 结构化输出 + AI优化 + 上下文感知\n- 本王测试：能搜到OpenClaw 2026.2.17发布、创始人加入OpenAI\n\n// VISUAL\nA search bar with \"OpenClaw最新更新\" typed in, results popping out with live news cards. Teal green accents.\n\n// LAYOUT\nSearch visual centered, bullet points below, large headline at top.\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":211,"output":1115,"cacheRead":85560,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86886,"cost":{"input":2.11e-8,"output":2.23e-7,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":2.441e-7}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772872564501}}
