s/scripts/text_to_srt.py\n\t删除：     skills/tts/scripts/third_party_sender.sh\n\t删除：     skills/tts/scripts/tts.sh\n\t删除：     skills/video-translation/SKILL.md\n\t删除：     skills/video-translation/scripts/replace_audio.sh\n\t删除：     skills/video-translation/scripts/srt_to_duck.py\n\n未跟踪的文件:\n  （使用 \"git add <文件>...\" 以包含要提交的内容）\n\t.claude/\n\t.qoder/\n\t.trae/\n\tskills/characteristic-voice\n\tskills/chat-with-anyone\n\tskills/daily-news-caster\n\tskills/template-skill\n\tskills/tts\n\tskills/video-translation\n\n修改尚未加入提交（使用 \"git add\" 和/或 \"git commit -a\"）\nNo git LFS","cwd":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772875680838}}
