{"type":"message","id":"775773b4","parentId":"3f27c0eb","timestamp":"2026-03-07T09:31:05.913Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完美！语音发出去了！\n\n总结一下今天的成果：\n1. ✅ 试水 baoyu-slide-deck 成功，完整生成12张PPT\n2. ✅ 装了 NoizAI 的6个语音技能\n3. ✅ 配了 Noiz API Key，生成了虾王的语音\n4. ✅ 用 OpenClaw 自带的 tts 直接把语音发你了\n\n今天的活干完了！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":145,"output":101,"cacheRead":121912,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122158,"cost":{"input":1.45e-8,"output":2.0200000000000002e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":3.47e-8}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772875843561}}
{"type":"message","id":"ca0b26aa","parentId":"775773b4","timestamp":"2026-03-07T09:31:41.384Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b558b490830a4b353b43f773765b\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-07 17:31 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\"\n}\n```\n\n我没收到语音条，飞书语音条正确的发送方式：\n上传文件：file_type=opus（不是 mp3），需要 receive_id_type=chat_id 和 receive_id\n发送消息：msg_type=audio，receive_id_type=chat_id，content 包含 file_key 和 duration"}],"timestamp":1772875901380}}
