{"type":"message","id":"4f4d4f0f","parentId":"90ba6476","timestamp":"2026-03-07T10:02:18.104Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"哦，这个 app_id/app_secret 无效——没关系，换个思路：你刚才不是已经收到 OpenClaw 自带 tts 发的语音条了吗？\n\n今天的主要任务都完成了：\n1. ✅ baoyu-slide-deck 试水成功，完整12张PPT\n2. ✅ NoizAI 6个语音技能全装好\n3. ✅ Noiz API Key 配置好，能生成语音了\n\n语音条的事儿要么等你换个有效的飞书 app_id/app_secret，要么下次再搞？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":288,"output":119,"cacheRead":129336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129743,"cost":{"input":2.88e-8,"output":2.38e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":5.26e-8}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772877707266}}
