{"type":"message","id":"71269abd","parentId":"55c6cabb","timestamp":"2026-03-07T10:03:03.409Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"可以！NoizAI 的 `tts` 技能支持声音克隆——你给我一段你的参考音频（至少10秒），我就能克隆你的音色，生成虾王的语音！\n\n你想试试吗？把你的一段说话录音发给我就行。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":99785,"output":57,"cacheRead":30264,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130106,"cost":{"input":0.000009978500000000001,"output":1.1400000000000001e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000099899}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772877754963}}
{"type":"message","id":"4b07b36c","parentId":"71269abd","timestamp":"2026-03-07T10:04:01.318Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/media/inbound/å_å---c2443642-bc98-4fd3-b183-f0173d4b7cca (audio/wav) | /Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/media/inbound/å_å---c2443642-bc98-4fd3-b183-f0173d4b7cca]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b558bce3f18acb315822202575c8\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-07 18:04 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\"\n}\n```\n\n[File: /Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/media/inbound/å_å---c2443642-bc98-4fd3-b183-f0173d4b7cca]"}],"timestamp":1772877841315}}
