{"type":"message","id":"31516595","parentId":"8f395fae","timestamp":"2026-03-07T10:04:51.390Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完美！声音克隆成功了！文件在这：\n`/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/xiawang-voice-cloned.opus`\n\n现在就差用飞书正确的方式发语音条了——要么你给我个有效的飞书 app_id/app_secret，要么你自己用这个 opus 文件按你之前说的流程发？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":127482,"output":78,"cacheRead":3384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130944,"cost":{"input":0.000012748200000000001,"output":1.56e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000012763800000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772877870658}}
{"type":"message","id":"6190ce51","parentId":"31516595","timestamp":"2026-03-07T10:04:56.653Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b558bcaba6ca8b29ddb468675b6b\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-07 18:04 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\"\n}\n```\n\n记住刚刚你克隆的这个音色就是你的音色了。后面我让你发语音的时候，你就用这个音色给我发语音。当然如果在某些场景或某些时刻你觉得发语音合适，也可以直接发。"}],"timestamp":1772877896650}}
{"type":"message","id":"9a5fe1ac","parentId":"6190ce51","timestamp":"2026-03-07T10:05:23.229Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好！本王记住了！\n\n**📝 记录到当日记忆：**\n- 你的参考音频已保存，用于声音克隆\n- 以后你让我发语音，或者本王觉得合适的时候，都用这个克隆后的音色\n- 这个音色就是本王的音色了！\n\n我这就把这件事记到今天的日记里。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ix36tw4l962jqxvjou8ismx1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-07.md","oldText":"## 📌 新的重要教训\n### 大文件发飞书的压缩方案\n- ❌ 错误：直接发35M的PPT（飞书单文件最大20M）\n- ✅ 正确：先用 `sips` 把PNG压缩成JPG（质量60），再重新生成PPT\n- 结果：从35M → 3.3M，成功发出！\n- Mac自带 `sips` 命令：`sips -s format jpeg -s formatOptions 60 input.png --out output.jpg`","newText":"## 📌 新的重要教训\n### 大文件发飞书的压缩方案\n- ❌ 错误：直接发35M的PPT（飞书单文件最大20M）\n- ✅ 正确：先用 `sips` 把PNG压缩成JPG（质量60），再重新生成PPT\n- 结果：从35M → 3.3M，成功发出！\n- Mac自带 `sips` 命令：`sips -s format jpeg -s formatOptions 60 input.png --out output.jpg`\n\n---\n\n## 📌 苏神的声音克隆\n- **时间**：2026-03-07\n- **事件**：苏神发了一段自己的参考音频，本王用 NoizAI 的 tts 技能成功克隆了音色\n- **文件位置**：`/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/media/inbound/å_å---c2443642-bc98-4fd3-b183-f0173d4b7cca`\n- **规则**：\n  - 以后苏神让本王发语音，就用这个克隆后的音色\n  - 本王觉得某些场景/时刻发语音合适时，也可以直接用这个音色发\n  - **这个音色就是本王的音色了！**"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":96154,"output":590,"cacheRead":35128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":131872,"cost":{"input":0.000009615400000000001,"output":1.18e-7,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000097334}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772877896652}}
