{"type":"message","id":"d49666df","parentId":"76cd4086","timestamp":"2026-03-07T10:06:25.459Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b558bc4ccc0a8b3d686975576b73\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-07 18:06 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\"\n}\n```\n\n你认真排查一下并解决，我真的想听你给我发飞书语音条。\n飞书语音条正确的发送方式：\n上传文件：file_type=opus（不是 mp3），需要 receive_id_type=chat_id 和 receive_id\n发送消息：msg_type=audio，receive_id_type=chat_id，content 包含 file_key 和 duration"}],"timestamp":1772877985423}}
