{"type":"message","id":"ee0437a1","parentId":"3d758c79","timestamp":"2026-03-07T10:43:48.689Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ukkinhlpsdd7aalmxc7hr82d","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"usage: agent-reach [-h] [-v] [--version]\n                   {setup,install,configure,doctor,uninstall,check-update,watch,version} ...\n\n👁️ Give your AI Agent eyes to see the entire internet\n\npositional arguments:\n  {setup,install,configure,doctor,uninstall,check-update,watch,version}\n                        Available commands\n    setup               Interactive configuration wizard\n    install             One-shot installer with flags\n    configure           Set a config value or auto-extract from browser\n    doctor              Check platform availability\n    uninstall           Remove all Agent Reach config, tokens, and skill files\n    check-update        Check for new versions and changes\n    watch               Quick health check + update check (for scheduled\n                        tasks)\n    version             Show version\n\noptions:\n  -h, --help            show this help message and exit\n  -v, --verbose         Show debug logs\n  --version             show program's version number and exit"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":231,"aggregated":"usage: agent-reach [-h] [-v] [--version]\n                   {setup,install,configure,doctor,uninstall,check-update,watch,version} ...\n\n👁️ Give your AI Agent eyes to see the entire internet\n\npositional arguments:\n  {setup,install,configure,doctor,uninstall,check-update,watch,version}\n                        Available commands\n    setup               Interactive configuration wizard\n    install             One-shot installer with flags\n    configure           Set a config value or auto-extract from browser\n    doctor              Check platform availability\n    uninstall           Remove all Agent Reach config, tokens, and skill files\n    check-update        Check for new versions and changes\n    watch               Quick health check + update check (for scheduled\n                        tasks)\n    version             Show version\n\noptions:\n  -h, --help            show this help message and exit\n  -v, --verbose         Show debug logs\n  --version             show program's version number and exit","cwd":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772880228659}}
