{"type":"message","id":"07835fd5","parentId":"b13e3761","timestamp":"2026-03-07T10:44:16.735Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5atkihcg0fichb8a66t0dtg8","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"👁️  Agent Reach 状态\n========================================\n\n✅ 装好即用：\n  ⚠️  GitHub 仓库和代码 — gh CLI 未安装。安装：https://cli.github.com\n  ❌ YouTube 视频和字幕 — yt-dlp 未安装。安装：pip install yt-dlp\n  ✅ RSS/Atom 订阅源 — 可读取 RSS/Atom 源\n  ❌ 全网语义搜索 — mcporter 已装但 Exa 未配置。运行：\n  mcporter config add exa https://mcp.exa.ai/mcp\n  ✅ 任意网页 — 通过 Jina Reader 读取任意网页（curl https://r.jina.ai/URL）\n\n🔍 搜索（mcporter 即可解锁）：\n  ✅ Twitter/X 推文 — 完整可用（读取、搜索推文）\n  ⬜ Reddit 帖子和评论 — 无代理。服务器 IP 可能被 Reddit 封锁。配置代理：\n  agent-reach configure proxy http://user:pass@ip:port\n  ⬜ B站视频和字幕 — yt-dlp 未安装。安装：pip install yt-dlp\n\n🔧 配置后可用：\n  ⬜ 小红书笔记 — mcporter 已装但小红书 MCP 未配置。运行：\n  docker run -d --name xiaohongshu-mcp -p 18060:18060 --platform linux/amd64 xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp\n  # ARM64 also: build from source: https://github.com/xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp\n  mcporter config add xiaohongshu http://localhost:18060/mcp\n  ⬜ 抖音短视频 — mcporter 已装但抖音 MCP 未配置。运行：\n  pip install douyin-mcp-server\n  # 启动服务后：\n  mcporter config add douyin http://localhost:18070/mcp\n  ⬜ LinkedIn 职业社交 — mcporter 已装但 LinkedIn MCP 未配置。运行：\n  pip install linkedin-scraper-mcp\n  mcporter config add linkedin http://localhost:3000/mcp\n  ⬜ Boss直聘职位搜索 — mcporter 已装但 Boss直聘 MCP 未配置。\n  详见 https://github.com/mucsbr/mcp-bosszp\n  ✅ 微信公众号文章 — 完整可用（搜索 + 阅读公众号文章）\n\n状态：4/13 个渠道可用\n运行 `agent-reach setup` 解锁更多渠道"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5610,"aggregated":"👁️  Agent Reach 状态\n========================================\n\n✅ 装好即用：\n  ⚠️  GitHub 仓库和代码 — gh CLI 未安装。安装：https://cli.github.com\n  ❌ YouTube 视频和字幕 — yt-dlp 未安装。安装：pip install yt-dlp\n  ✅ RSS/Atom 订阅源 — 可读取 RSS/Atom 源\n  ❌ 全网语义搜索 — mcporter 已装但 Exa 未配置。运行：\n  mcporter config add exa https://mcp.exa.ai/mcp\n  ✅ 任意网页 — 通过 Jina Reader 读取任意网页（curl https://r.jina.ai/URL）\n\n🔍 搜索（mcporter 即可解锁）：\n  ✅ Twitter/X 推文 — 完整可用（读取、搜索推文）\n  ⬜ Reddit 帖子和评论 — 无代理。服务器 IP 可能被 Reddit 封锁。配置代理：\n  agent-reach configure proxy http://user:pass@ip:port\n  ⬜ B站视频和字幕 — yt-dlp 未安装。安装：pip install yt-dlp\n\n🔧 配置后可用：\n  ⬜ 小红书笔记 — mcporter 已装但小红书 MCP 未配置。运行：\n  docker run -d --name xiaohongshu-mcp -p 18060:18060 --platform linux/amd64 xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp\n  # ARM64 also: build from source: https://github.com/xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp\n  mcporter config add xiaohongshu http://localhost:18060/mcp\n  ⬜ 抖音短视频 — mcporter 已装但抖音 MCP 未配置。运行：\n  pip install douyin-mcp-server\n  # 启动服务后：\n  mcporter config add douyin http://localhost:18070/mcp\n  ⬜ LinkedIn 职业社交 — mcporter 已装但 LinkedIn MCP 未配置。运行：\n  pip install linkedin-scraper-mcp\n  mcporter config add linkedin http://localhost:3000/mcp\n  ⬜ Boss直聘职位搜索 — mcporter 已装但 Boss直聘 MCP 未配置。\n  详见 https://github.com/mucsbr/mcp-bosszp\n  ✅ 微信公众号文章 — 完整可用（搜索 + 阅读公众号文章）\n\n状态：4/13 个渠道可用\n运行 `agent-reach setup` 解锁更多渠道","cwd":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772880256687}}
