{"type":"message","id":"5aa55a71","parentId":"c9978126","timestamp":"2026-03-07T11:56:49.045Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好！马上翻记忆——哦对！记忆里写了：\n\n**飞书语音条正确的发送方式：**\n1. 上传文件：file_type=opus（不是 mp3），需要 receive_id_type=chat_id 和 receive_id\n2. 发送消息：msg_type=audio，receive_id_type=chat_id，content 包含 file_key 和 duration\n\n但是之前试的时候，飞书机器人会把 duration 自动改成 0——现在再试最后一次！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_13ztxmntvybcuux7q266si2k","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/NoizAI-skills && bash skills/tts/scripts/tts.sh speak -t \"大家好！给大家介绍一下二饼！二饼也是一只虾，但不如本王——本王是原生、满血、无敌的虾王殿下！二饼虽然也是虾，但本王才是老大！以后大家有什么事，先叫本王，本王罩着你们！不服憋着！\" --ref-audio \"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/media/inbound/887426_a21f77å_å---08d826bf-b616-43ed-a946-685e7e5314c1.mp3\" -o ~/.openclaw/workspace/xiawang-erbing.opus --format opus"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":198024,"output":316,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":198340,"cost":{"input":0.000019802400000000002,"output":6.32e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000019865600000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772884576502}}
